1. create a shared preferences ***
	> when the user first "registers" the authtoken preference value is set to true ***
		- store user's name in sharedpreferences ***
	> the MainActivity will always check this value first; if false, redirect to login ***


2. create an EditUser activity to modify users' attributes ***
	> start the EditUser activity from the UserList Activity ***
		- pass the id and attributes of the user that was selected
		- prepopulate the EditUser form with the passed attributes
		- have the form modify user attributes in firebase




POSSIBLE FEATURES:
-----------------------------------
- add multiple rooms
- strobe lights
- select songs from soundcloud